  "body": "\r\nThis icon is the visual mark for the [XanaNode](/node/xananode) theme.\r\n\r\nThe crossing lines and central node are meant to suggest [typed relationships](/node/typed-relationships), visible lineage, and a substrate whose meaning comes from the connections between things rather than from isolated documents.\n",
